{"tid":2060104,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"連登 PR 研究","createTime":"2020-06-11T11:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T21:02:47.000Z","uid":160747,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9f45a33b8f3c96a09a23d64e6e2bc227f39b39a2","tid":2060104,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:30:03.000Z","msg":"大家可以睇下我之前開既兩個撚PR既post<br />\n大概內容都係叫人入警隊做徐步高<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 點解之前徐步高係英雄個post有成千正評而依加叫人做徐步高就咁多負評？ </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 大家好明顯見到一開post就會有人用圖片曲解你既內容</span><br />\n<br />\n當我係第二個post開始pin點解之前徐步高係英雄個post有成千正評而依加叫人做徐步高就咁多負評？嗰時立即冇曬PR出黎留言加負評，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以PR係一定有滲透連登 </span><br />\n<br />\nPR目的<br />\n1.限制風向，同帶動風向去佢想佢既地方<br />\n2.令人唔敢再提有爭議性既野，避免單機<br />\n<br />\nPR策略<br />\n1.搶做第一個留言限制討論方向同帶風向<br />\n2.多分身，頭五六個留言一定要負面<br />\n<br />\n解決方法<br />\n1.如果你要開有爭議性既題目必須要有圖片黎滿足香港人既即食文化<br />\n2.要自己有多幾個分身"},{"pid":"5f2c697a584d2a5edcdc4898e503b989a23e54fd","tid":2060104,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"1a47231fb6be6b4d14bd258de04cbb27df73709a","tid":2060104,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:31:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"667e81e44bc610165afaf715712f027e4ec14283","tid":2060104,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebbd95c368860f29ecec440eca781e1f6d278143","tid":2060104,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:31:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e259758066af30412b913317af73ecf1c0dc7ed5","tid":2060104,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:32:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c85c798d1e7b956159839e3abc7e5d4771b9d37b","tid":2060104,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4090efccd3077870fc654cb0e5de1b2897e97157","tid"